name: Embraced
description:
- Wall #3 -

The tranquility of trusting what surrounds us, being part of the whole.

I’ve painted this calm dude in a wall at the side of the train rails in Santa Fe, Argentina.
Then erased some parts and added some digital animation replacing the erased parts, maintaining the original design.
